nodes.text: Z23-Y75 was an OOM command battle droid, a droid model in the OOM-series of battle droids, who was manufactured by the Baktoid Combat Automata company to serve in the droid army of the galactic corporation: the Trade Federation. Z23-Y75 fought for the Federation as a commander sometime before the Clone Wars in 22 BBY. As with all OOM battle droids, Z23-Y75 was 1.91 meters tall, had masculine programming, and wielded an E-5 blaster rifle. The droid's head and some other parts of his body were colored white, while the rest was brown.

Z23-Y75 first appears in the 2001 PC video game Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds, and also appears in its 2002 expansion Clone Campaigns. In the video games, Z23-Y75 only appears in the scenario editor mode, in which he is a unique unit that can be placed in custom player-made levels. In the skirmish mode of the game, where the player can play against computer players or other people, Z23-Y75's name can be randomly generated as the commander for the Trade Federation.
